OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1779732663
OL,3,CIsle of Man ferry service to Dublin
OL,4,Ccancelled over summer and autumn
OL,6,FThe Isle of Man Steam Packet Company
OL,7,Fhas cancelled its summer-autumn ferry
OL,8,Fservice to Dublin, citing ''on-going
OL,9,Finfrastructure disruption".
OL,11,FThere will be no service to the Irish
OL,12,Fcapital from 23 july to 1 October
OL,13,F2026, though sailings will continue as
OL,14,Fnormal until 19 July.
OL,16,FBut the company insisted the move did
OL,17,Fnot signal a "withdrawal" from Dublin.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
