PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1779732663
OL,3,CIsle of Man ferry service to Dublin
OL,4,Ccancelled over summer and autumn
OL,6,FThe announcement will be a blow to the
OL,7,Fthousands of motorbike enthusiasts who
OL,8,Ftravel to the Isle of Man from Ireland
OL,9,Ffor races over the summer.
OL,11,FThe service from Douglas to Dublin was
OL,12,Fonly announced in November 2025.
OL,14,FA company statement said
OL,15,Finfrastructure disruption affecting
OL,16,FHolyhead Port in North Wales had
OL,17,Fresulted in reduced berths and sailing
OL,18,Fslots across the wider Irish Sea
OL,19,Fnetwork, including Dublin.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1779732663
OL,3,CIsle of Man ferry service to Dublin
OL,4,Ccancelled over summer and autumn
OL,6,FThe company added it had spent recent
OL,7,Fmonths exploring a range of
OL,8,Fcontingency options in a bid to
OL,9,Fmaintain the route.
OL,11,FManaging Director Brian Thomson said:
OL,12,F"While these infrastructure challenges
OL,13,Fare outside the Company's control, our
OL,14,Fresponsibility is how we respond to
OL,15,Fthem. This has been an extremely
OL,16,Fdifficult decision because we
OL,17,Frecognise the importance of the Dublin
OL,18,Froute not just for passengers, but for
OL,19,Fbusiness and wider relationships
OL,20,Fbetween the Isle of Man and Ireland.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1779732663
OL,3,CIsle of Man ferry service to Dublin
OL,4,Ccancelled over summer and autumn
OL,6,F"The Company has worked closely with
OL,7,FDublin Port to explore potential
OL,8,Fsolutions to the ongoing berth
OL,9,Favailability constraints, but has not
OL,10,Fidentified an option that provides an
OL,11,Foperationally sustainable solution
OL,12,Fwhile maintaining the reliability of
OL,13,Fthe wider network.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1779732663
OL,3,CIsle of Man ferry service to Dublin
OL,4,Ccancelled over summer and autumn
OL,6,F"As a result, the Company will
OL,7,Fcontinue to focus on providing
OL,8,Fresilient and dependable services
OL,9,Facross core routes, while maintaining
OL,10,Fconnectivity for passengers and
OL,11,Ffreight customers travelling to and
OL,12,Ffrom Ireland via the existing Larne
OL,13,Fservice.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1779732663
OL,3,CIsle of Man ferry service to Dublin
OL,4,Ccancelled over summer and autumn
OL,6,F"The impact of the change is limited
OL,7,Fto a relatively small number of
OL,8,Fsailings and customers, with
OL,9,Falternative travel options remaining
OL,10,Favailable through the Company's Larne
OL,11,Foperations. From July, the Larne route
OL,12,Fwill also expand to three sailings per
OL,13,Fweek year-round, further strengthening
OL,14,Fconnectivity and capacity for
OL,15,Fpassengers and freight.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1779732663
OL,3,CIsle of Man ferry service to Dublin
OL,4,Ccancelled over summer and autumn
OL,6,F"We have taken the decision to cancel
OL,7,Fthe route while we continue working
OL,8,Fwith port authorities and stakeholders
OL,9,Fto secure improved operating
OL,10,Fconditions and more suitable berth
OL,11,Faccess.
OL,13,F"This is not a withdrawal from Dublin.
OL,14,FWe remain committed to the route and
OL,15,Fsailings via Dublin for Spring 2027
OL,16,F(inclusive of TT) are still available
OL,17,Fto book."
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
