OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1779732663
OL,3,CIsle of Man ferry service to Dublin
OL,4,Ccancelled over summer and autumn
OL,6,FCustomers already booked on affected
OL,7,Fsailings are being contacted directly
OL,8,Fand offered the option of transferring
OL,9,Fto alternative Isle of Man Steam
OL,10,FPacket Company services free of charge
OL,11,For receiving a full refund.
